## Layer order (Clean Architecture)

Build and read in this order; dependencies point inward:

```
entity → repository contract → use case → state/view-model → UI
```

- **domain** (`{{SOURCE_DIR}}/<domain>`): entities, value objects, repository interfaces, use cases. Imports nothing outward.
- **data** (`{{SOURCE_DIR}}/<data>`): repository implementations, data sources. Implements domain interfaces.
- **presentation** (`{{SOURCE_DIR}}/<presentation>`): state + UI. Imports domain only — never data directly.

